original_title: Spaniens grüner Norden – Vom Jakobsweg bis zum Ende der Welt
overview: A mixture of Ireland, Norway and the Caribbean - that is Galicia, Spain's green north. Judith Rakers explores the unique nature between rough cliffs, green primeval forests and island paradises with dream beaches. On the Way of St. James, she makes a pilgrimage from Santiago de Compostela to the end of the world.
title: Spaniens grüner Norden – Vom Jakobsweg bis zum Ende der Welt
